| Encryption Type | CDK Option                     | Key Management        |
|----------------|--------------------------------|------------------------|
| SSE-S3         | `s3.BucketEncryption.S3_MANAGED` | Amazon S3-managed      |
| SSE-KMS        | `s3.BucketEncryption.KMS`        | AWS KMS (customer-managed) |

